citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:15 pm to 2:45 pm
on November 29, 2022. During this time the inspector waited at the facility for 30 minutes and called the licensee's cell
phone number and left a message.
End Section
